Summary of the conformance test
The accessibility conformance test was conducted using the WAVE browser extension. The page includes images, product configuration controls, pricing, reviews, and technical specifications. Major issues identified include missing alternative text, low contrast, unlabelled form elements, incorrect heading structure, and improper table markup.
