Missing alternative text	 	Images without alt attributes prevent screen-reader users from understanding essential product information.	Add descriptive alt text such as: <img src='product-black.png' alt='Product X smartwatch, black edition'>
	Broken WCAG level: WCAG 1.1.1 Non-text Content — Level A

Low color contrast	 	Low contrast makes text unreadable for users with visual impairments.	Ensure contrast ratios meet 4.5:1 for normal text and 3:1 for large text.
	Broken WCAG level: WCAG 1.4.3 Contrast (Minimum) — Level AA

